---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import map from '../assets/map.jpg';
import rings from '../assets/rings.png';

import { Comments } from '../components/Comments';
---

<Layout title={`Our Wedding Day!`}>
  <div class='relative min-h-screen w-full'>
    <div
      class='absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#548CB3] to-[#8DC8E7]'
    >
    </div>

    <div class='absolute z-10 inset-0 overflow-hidden'>
      <div class='cloud-1'></div>
      <div class='cloud-2'></div>
      <div class='cloud-3'></div>
    </div>

    <div class='relative z-50 px-4 md:px-20 py-14 md:py-40 space-y-10'>
      <div
        class='container mx-auto px-4 md:px-10 pt-40 pb-20 max-w-4xl space-y-14 border-[20px] xl:border-[40px] border-white/20'
      >
        <div class='text-center text-white space-y-10 w-full'>
          <h1 class='text-8xl font-parisienne font-bold'>Reksa & Resti</h1>
        </div>

        <div class='text-center space-y-2 text-white'>
          <h3 class='text-lg font-normal'>Dilaksanakan</h3>
          <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>Sabtu, 12 April 2025</h2>

          <div class='space-y-1 my-10'>
            <p class='text-xl font-normal'>Acara: 09:00 - 14:00</p>
          </div>

          <a
            href='https://calendar.app.google/4haEsVDWU5iHmRTA8'
            class='rounded-full cursor-pointer transition-all ease-in-out duration-300 hover:scale-125 text-black font-medium text-sm border-2 border-[#CBCBCB]/20 px-4 py-3 shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-[#EAEAEA]'
            target='_blank'
          >
            Simpan di Kalender
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class='text-center space-y-6 text-white'>
          <h4 class='text-xl font-medium'>Bismillahirrahmaanirrahiim</h4>
          <p class='text-base font-normal'>
            Maha Suci Allah Subhanahu Wa Ta’ala yang telah menciptakan
            makhluk-Nya berpasang-pasangan. Dengan memohon Rahmat dan Ridho
            Allah Subahanahu Wa Ta’ala, Kami bermaksud mengundang
            Bapak/Ibu/Saudara/i dalam acara Pernikahan Kami.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class='flex flex-col gap-10 items-center justify-center'>
          <div class='h-fit w-fit'>
            <img src={rings.src} class='h-full w-full' alt='A rings.' />
          </div>
          <div
            class='grid grid-cols-1 md:gap-4 gap-y-10 auto-rows-fr md:grid-cols-2'
          >
            <div class='text-center text-white space-y-3'>
              <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>Reksa Sarmedi Ma’mur</h3>
              <p class='text-sm font-normal'>
                <span>Putra dari Alm Bpk. Sarmedi Ma’mur</span>
                <br />
                <span>& Ibu Santi Sri Mulyati</span>
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class='text-center text-white space-y-2'>
              <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold'>Resti Meidiyani Dimyati</h3>
              <p class='text-sm font-normal'>
                <span>Putri dari Alm Bpk. Didin Dimyati</span>
                <br />
                <span>& Ibu Lilis Setiawati</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <a href='https://maps.app.goo.gl/s4NFsbRVH1bXY3Lv7' target='_blank'>
            <div
              class='bg-blend-multiply relative w-full flex justify-center items-center cursor-pointer isolate hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 bg-[length:300%_250%] md:bg-[length:300%_400%] bg-[position:45%_45%] md:bg-[position:40%_59%] border-4 border-[#EAEAEA] rounded-3xl bg-clip-border shadow-xl h-64 bg-no-repeat'
            >
              <div
                class='rounded-2xl transition-all gap-10 duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm hover:backdrop-blur-none bg-gradient-to-r from-white from-20% to-white/20 to-50% flex flex-col h-full w-full px-6 py-12 md:px-8 md:py-10 justify-between group'
              >
                <div class='flex-1 space-y-2'>
                  <span
                    class='text-xl group-hover:underline group-hover:text-[#103CC4]'
                  >
                    Lokasi
                  </span>
                  <h4
                    class='text-4xl font-bold group-hover:underline group-hover:text-[#103CC4]'
                  >
                    Taman Kopi Serang
                  </h4>
                </div>

                <span class='group-hover:underline group-hover:text-[#103CC4]'>
                  Lihat map
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class='text-white space-y-6 text-center'>
          <h1 class='font-parisienne text-4xl'>Wedding Gift</h1>
          <p>
            Do'a restu anda merupakan karunia yang sangat berarti bagi kami. Dan
            jika memberi adalah bentuk kasih, kini dapat mengirimkannya dari
            mana saja. Terimakasih
          </p>

          <a
            href='/gift'
            class='transition-all ease-in-out duration-300 hover:scale-125 cursor-pointer text-center px-10 py-3 bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-700 to-zinc-800 border border-zinc-600 shadow text-white rounded-full drop-shadow-md'
          >
            Wedding Gift
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class='text-center text-white space-y-6'>
          <h6 class='text-xl'>Qs. Ar-Rum: 21</h6>
          <p class='text-base'>
            وَمِنْ ءَايَٰتِهِۦٓ أَنْ خَلَقَ لَكُم مِّنْ أَنفُسِكُمْ أَزْوَٰجًا
            لِّتَسْكُنُوٓا۟ إِلَيْهَا وَجَعَلَ بَيْنَكُم مَّوَدَّةً وَرَحْمَةً ۚ
            إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَءَايَٰتٍ لِّقَوْمٍ يَتَفَكَّرُونَ
          </p>
          <p class='text-base'>
            "Dan di antara tanda-tanda kekuasaan-Nya ialah Dia menciptakan
            untukmu isteri-isteri dari jenismu sendiri, supaya kamu cenderung
            dan merasa tenteram kepadanya, dan dijadikan-Nya diantaramu rasa
            kasih dan sayang. Sesungguhnya pada yang demikian itu benar-benar
            terdapat tanda-tanda bagi kaum yang berfikir."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class='text-center text-white space-y-4'>
          <h1 class='text-xl font-semibold'>Terimakasih</h1>
          <p class='text-base font-light isolate'>
            Demikian Kami sampaikan Undangan ini, mohon maaf apabila terdapat
            kesalahan kata. Terimakasih atas segala doa dan harapannya.
          </p>
        </div>

        <Comments client:load />
      </div>

      <p class='text-white text-center w-full'>
        12.04.2025 <span class='font-semibold'>Resti & Reksa</span>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
<style>
  /* body {
    overflow: hidden;
  } */

  .cloud-1 {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    width: 260em;
    height: 50%;
    background: url('../assets/Clouds.png') 0 100% repeat-x;
    -webkit-animation: cloudLoop 250s linear infinite;
    animation: cloudLoop 250s linear infinite;
    z-index: 2;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.8;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .cloud-1 {
      height: 40%;
    }
  }

  .cloud-2 {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 260em;
    height: 65%;
    background: url('../assets/Clouds.png') 0 100% repeat-x;
    -webkit-animation: cloudLoop-1 200s linear infinite;
    animation: cloudLoop-1 200s linear infinite;
    z-index: 3;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.3;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .cloud-2 {
      height: 50%;
    }
  }

  .cloud-3 {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    width: 260em;
    height: 80%;
    background: url('../assets/Clouds.png') 0 100% repeat-x;
    -webkit-animation: cloudLoop-2 150s linear infinite;
    animation: cloudLoop-2 150s linear infinite;
    z-index: 4;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.2;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .cloud-3 {
      height: 60%;
    }
  }

  @-webkit-keyframes cloudLoop {
    0% {
      transform: translate3d(0%, 0, 0);
    }

    100% {
      transform: translate3d(-50%, 0, 0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes cloudLoop {
    0% {
      transform: translate3d(0%, 0, 0);
    }

    100% {
      transform: translate3d(-50%, 0, 0);
    }
  }

  @-webkit-keyframes cloudLoop-1 {
    0% {
      transform: translate3d(-10%, 0, 0);
    }

    100% {
      transform: translate3d(-40%, 0, 0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes cloudLoop-1 {
    0% {
      transform: translate3d(-10%, 0, 0);
    }

    100% {
      transform: translate3d(-40%, 0, 0);
    }
  }

  @-webkit-keyframes cloudLoop-2 {
    0% {
      transform: translate3d(20%, 0, 0);
    }

    100% {
      transform: translate3d(-30%, 0, 0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes cloudLoop-2 {
    0% {
      transform: translate3d(20%, 0, 0);
    }

    100% {
      transform: translate3d(-30%, 0, 0);
    }
  }
</style>
